### 
```mermaid
classDiagram
    class Project {
        +project_id: string
        +name: string
        +status: ProjectStatus
        +files: List[Dict]
        +ontology: Dict
        +graph_id: string
    }
    
    class SimulationManager {
        +create_simulation()
        +prepare_simulation()
        +get_run_instructions()
    }
    
    class ReportAgent {
        +plan_outline()
        +generate_report()
        +interview_agents()
    }
    
    class GraphBuilderService {
        +create_graph()
        +add_text_batches()
        +get_graph_data()
    }
    
    Project --> GraphBuilderService
    SimulationManager --> ReportAgent
    SimulationManager --> GraphBuilderService
    ReportAgent --> GraphBuilderService
```
